name: Natural_Evolution_Enemies_Redux
title: Natural Evolution Enemies (Redux)

description: All things Alien! Adds new Enemies and updates to Biter/Spitters Spawners. If you want a more of a challenge than what Vinalla can offer you... Part of the N.E. Mods, but can be used as Standalone. Please visit home page for more details. This Redux version aims to improve UPS and make the game more playable on death worlds
